{"article_id":"eko0lzijcuKhQ3KT","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Defense Secretary Mark Esper has fired the Navy ' s top official ,","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"ending a stunning clash between President Donald Trump and top military leadership over the fate of a SEAL","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"accused of war crimes in Iraq .","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"Esper said Sunday","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that he had lost confidence in Navy Secretary Richard Spencer","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"and alleged","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"that Spencer proposed a deal with the White House behind his back","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"to resolve the SEAL ' s case .","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"Trump has championed the matter of Navy Chief Petty Officer Edward Gallagher ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"who was acquitted of murder in the stabbing death of an Islamic State militant captive","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"but convicted of posing with the corpse while in Iraq in 2017 .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Spencer ' s firing was a dramatic turn in the fast-changing and politically charged controversy .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"It exposed fissures in Trump ' s relationship with the highest ranks of the U.S. military","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"and raised questions about the appropriate role of a commander in chief in matters of military justice .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Gallagher was demoted from chief petty officer to a 1st class petty officer after his conviction by a military jury .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Trump , however , restored Gallagher ' s rank this month .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"On Wednesday , the Navy had notified Gallagher","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that he would face a Navy SEAL review board","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"to determine","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"if he should be allowed to remain in the elite force .","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"While Trump then tweeted","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"that he would not allow the Navy to remove Gallagher from the SEALs","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"by taking away his Trident Pin ,","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"which designates a SEAL member ,","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"the White House told the Navy","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"it could proceed","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"as planned ,","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"according to a Navy officer","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"who spoke on condition of anonymity","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"to discuss internal matters .","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"That initially appeared to defuse the situation .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"The Navy SEAL review board was due to hear Gallagher ' s case on Dec. 2 .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"Spencer ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"speaking Saturday at an international security forum in Halifax , Nova Scotia ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"that he did not consider a tweet by Trump a formal order","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"to stop the Navy review board .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"`` I need a formal order","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"to act , ''","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Spencer said .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"He said of Trump ' s tweets ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"`` I do n't interpret them as a formal order . ''","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"But on Sunday , Esper said","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"he had learned","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"that Spencer had \" privately \" proposed to the White House","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"that Gallagher be allowed to retire in his current rank","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"and without losing his status as a SEAL .","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"Esper said","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Spencer had not told him of the proposal to the White House ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"causing him to lose \" trust and confidence . \"","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"A spokesperson for Spencer , Navy Cmdr . Sarah Higgins , said","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Spencer had no immediate comment .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"The White House did not provide details of Spencer ' s alleged private proposal regarding Gallagher .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"In yet another twist , Esper also directed on Sunday","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"that Gallagher be allowed to retire at the end of this month ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"and that the Navy review board","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"that was scheduled to hear his case","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"starting Dec. 2","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"be cancelled .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"At Esper ' s direction , Gallagher will be allowed to retire as a SEAL at his current rank .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"In a letter to Trump","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"acknowledging \" my termination , \"","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"Spencer said","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"he had concluded","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"that he and the president appear no longer to share the same understanding of \" the key principle of good order and discipline . \"","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"\" I can not in good conscience obey an order","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"I believe","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"violates the sacred oath","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"I took in the presence of my family , my flag and my faith","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"to support and defend the Constitution of the United States , \"","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"he wrote .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"He did not cite a specific order .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"Chief Pentagon spokesman Jonathan Hoffman said","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Esper ' s position had been that the Navy ' s disciplinary process should be allowed to \" play itself out objectively and deliberately . \"","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"\" However , at this point ,","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"given the events of the last few days , \"","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"Esper decided","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"that Gallagher should be allowed to retain his SEAL status ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Hoffman said .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"Esper had concluded","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"that Gallagher could not , under the circumstances , receive a fair shake from the Navy .","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"In the written statement , Esper said of Spencer :","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"\" I am deeply troubled by this conduct","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"shown by a senior DOD official .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Unfortunately , as a result","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"I have determined","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"that Secretary Spencer no longer has my confidence","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"to continue in his position .","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"I wish Richard well . ''","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"Gallagher ,","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"speaking Sunday on \" Fox & Friends , \"","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"alleged","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"the Navy was acting in retaliation .","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"\" They could have taken my Trident at any time","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"they wanted , \"","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"\" Now they ' re trying to take it","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"after the president restored my rank . \"","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"Those","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"who have their Trident pins removed","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"will no longer be SEALs","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"but could remain in the Navy .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"The Navy has revoked 154 Trident pins since 2011 .","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"Spencer , 65 , had served as Navy secretary since August 2017 .","depth":4},{"id":106,"text":"He was a Wall Street investment banker","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"and is a veteran of the Marine Corps .","depth":5},{"id":108,"text":"He and Esper were Pentagon peers during the period","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"that Esper served as Army secretary ,","depth":5},{"id":110,"text":"prior to being sworn in as defense secretary last July .","depth":4},{"id":111,"text":"In a series of tweets Sunday evening , Trump said","depth":4},{"id":112,"text":"he had been unhappy with the Navy ' s handling of the Gallagher case .","depth":4},{"id":113,"text":"\" Likewise , large cost overruns from past administration ' s contracting procedures were not addressed to my satisfaction , \"","depth":4},{"id":114,"text":"Trump added","depth":5},{"id":115,"text":"without specifics .","depth":5},{"id":116,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer , D-N.Y. , issued a statement","depth":4},{"id":117,"text":"saying","depth":5},{"id":118,"text":"Spencer \" did the right thing \"","depth":7},{"id":119,"text":"and \" should be proud of standing up to President Trump","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"when he was wrong ,","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"something","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"too many in this Administration and the Republican Party are scared to do .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"Good order , discipline , and morale among the Armed Services must transcend politics ,","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"and Secretary Spencer ' s commitment to these principles with not be forgotten . \"","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"Sen. Jim Inhofe , the Oklahoma Republican","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"who chairs the Armed Services Committee ,","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"Trump and Esper \" deserve to have a leadership team","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"who has their trust and confidence. \"","depth":7},{"id":130,"text":"He also acknowledged","depth":6},{"id":131,"text":"that he and Spencer had disagreed at times over the management of specific Navy programs .","depth":6},{"id":132,"text":"Trump said","depth":6},{"id":133,"text":"he was nominating Kenneth Braithwaite , a retired Navy rear admiral and the current U.S. ambassador to Norway ,","depth":7},{"id":134,"text":"to succeed Spencer .","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"In a tweet , Trump called Braithwaite \" a man of great achievement and success . \"","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":271,"left":246,"right":270,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":240,"right":245,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":151,"right":239,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":146,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":143,"right":145,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":138,"right":142,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":0,"right":137,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":139,"right":141,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":139,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":141,"left":5,"right":140,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":140,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":8,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":148,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":11,"right":147,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":149,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":239,"left":187,"right":238,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":187,"left":166,"right":186,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":165,"right":31,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":154,"right":164,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":154,"left":16,"right":153,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":153,"left":17,"right":152,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"attribution",